Endpoint to upload ISO metadata Usage Example:

import requests

dataset_id = 1 url = f”http://localhost:8080/api/v2/datasets/{dataset_id}/metadata” files=[

(‘metadata_file’,(‘metadata.xml’,open(‘/home/user/metadata.xml’,’rb’),’text/xml’))

] headers = {

‘Authorization’: ‘Basic dXNlcjpwYXNzd29yZA==’

} response = requests.request(“PUT”, url, payload={}, files=files)

cURL example: curl –location –request PUT ‘http://localhost:8000/api/v2/datasets/{dataset_id}/metadata’ –form ‘metadata_file=@/home/user/metadata.xml’
